{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":11,"day":27}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"欢呼胜利的十月","authors":["李瑛"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人们歌唱十月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选择了无数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好的字眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我歌唱十月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须使用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三倍壮丽的语言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年，多少月，多少天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张张撕落了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，对于我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象小鸟啄下一根根羽毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象大树落下一张张叶片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，我们是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党党员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺取了胜利的昨日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们眼前该怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻占明天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每晚，每晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我读罢毛主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻掩卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便不禁一次次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严肃地思虑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们党的命运——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，阳光—一雨雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无尽的关山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呵，你曾有光辉的过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，你将有怎样的明天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，我们失去了您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——伟大的领袖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该如何扫净面前这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷雾浓烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们信心百倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却又常常不能入眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和黎明悄悄谈心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们会用X光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用超声波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对党的肌体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行严格细致地检验；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，象外科医生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切除毒瘤一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清除党内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些隐患！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，胜利了！胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清除了“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底粉碎了他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篡党夺权的暗算！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一分一寸解放的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一锹一镐建设的家园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能想象，明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们将把你交给"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥饿，水火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镣铐，皮鞭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，胜利了，胜利了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以华主席为首的党中央"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"率领我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举清除了这些坏蛋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利了！胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，欢乐张开了翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声挣脱了锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯，一下子打开狂欢的闸门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使八亿颗心，春潮翻卷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯，使全世界资产阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直目瞪口呆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止不住瑟瑟发颤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯，使每一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都成了真正的节日；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使每口空气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也充满甘甜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯，染得大地如锦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开万朵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，云蒸霞蔚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气象万千！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，尽管经过了文化大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严峻的斗争呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何曾有丝毫稍减！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了警惕病菌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵入党的肌体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就要这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地检验："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的血液，党的心脏，党的肌腱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，胜利了！胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜了疾风暴雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们征服了惊雷怒电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争使我们的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻炼得何等矫健——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，它雄伟的体魄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，它宽厚的双肩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了这一光辉的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要到大街上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到天安门广场去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去尽兴地游行、呼喊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去擂动一千面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撼地的大鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去燃响一万挂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震天的响鞭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向周围的每一个同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，祝贺；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至刚刚诞生的婴儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我祝福你们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了睛空丽日的今天和明天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，大街上——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七岁的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦跳跳象小鸟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而七十岁的老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不禁激动得嘴唇微颤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们的发辫在旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子的歌声象飞泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐，击响了每一面大鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐，弹响了每一根琴弦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，北京城，幢幢高楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——千万面窗子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镶着数不清的笑脸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，朝霞鸽哨，晴空万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——如火的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞舞在每一寸空间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大会堂前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大理石的圆柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶天立地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琉璃瓦的飞檐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸九天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，仿佛也如此的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬眉吐气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此的辉煌、壮丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磅礴、威严！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从东长安街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到天安门广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又从纪念碑下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到博物馆前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长安街呵，快记下吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记下这灿烂的一页；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博物馆呵，快展出吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展出这革命的续篇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愧是毛主席缔造和培育的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承受过千万次炮火锤炼的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们成熟的党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，又胜利地经受了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次何等严峻的考验！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董存瑞同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们又炸毁了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你未炸完的敌堡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄继光同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们又堵住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你未堵完的枪眼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时呵，我不禁想起："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放北京城的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个欢乐的早晨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又不禁想起："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎了刘、林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级司令部的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些欢乐的夜晚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，红旗，花雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，人海，灯山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峥嵘岁月呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争连着胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利在召唤明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这严重危急的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您，劈波斩浪，力挽狂澜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的同志们、战友们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把这庄严的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻上大理石的石碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把它载入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的最重要的文献；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把它谱成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的乐曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把它写进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的诗篇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想得多么多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又想得多么远……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于这里发生的一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想说给几年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我新结识的伙伴——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大兴安岭的赤松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澜沧江畔的剑兰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉萨河谷的新犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江口外的白帆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我甚至想报告给你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴黎公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后撤出街垒的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机枪射手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最先冲进冬宫的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤卫队员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然那时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还没有来到人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但此刻，我和你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是战斗在同一条战线！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，披着满天星光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到家里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，顾不得洗脸、吃饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙打开："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《国家与革命》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《哥达纲领批判》；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙打开："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习，领会，钻研……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，党小组长同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向你汇报：我，还想写一百首诗篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我的小小的诗歌呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放开喉头歌唱吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱党的不朽的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱真理的凯旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱无产阶级战斗的幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱人民的春天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们生活得多么有声有色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么兴奋又多么庄严！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，狂欢的泪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却引起我严峻的思考；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"极度的兴奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越激起我对您更深的思念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着墙上悬挂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的照片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您用信任的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩望着我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样出色的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实践您殷切的心愿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从我知道了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的先烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战场上把第一滴血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，就选定了自己的位置——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了警惕党内外一切敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要永远守卫在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级阵地的前沿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象枪上忠诚的准星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象枪膛无畏的子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫先烈热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸染的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红旗飘扬在更高更高的峰巅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然我们无产阶级的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已迎风冒雪战斗过半个多世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就更相信它的明天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然我们伟大的人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已在铁砧上千锤百炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就更相信它的明天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然我们又有了当之无愧的领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就更相信它的明天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，我们将用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死地战斗，不息地劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充实它的分分秒秒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，我们将用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夯歌、汗水和报靶的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点染它的月月年年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来，一定属于我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利，一定属于我们；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如春天和花朵一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不会分离！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是斗争给予我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报偿和幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——呵，我们光辉灿烂的明天！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"捍卫毛泽东思想工人赤卫队上海总部（赤卫队）","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}